Scarlett Pomers https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scarlett_Pomers 0 Scarlett Noel Pomers (born November 28, 1988) is an American actress and singer-songwriter. Her most recognizable roles have been as Naomi Wildman on Star Trek: Voyager (1998–2001) and Kyra Hart on the television series Reba (2001–2007). Her debut EP, entitled Insane, was released January 7, 2010. Scarlett_Noel_Pomers ( born November_28_,_1988 ) is an_American_actress_and_singer-songwriter .
